trans-unit.source: An activity used to explicitly invoke the compensation handler of a <xref href="System.Activities.Statements.CompensableActivity"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En aktivitet som används för att explicit anropa kompensationshanteraren av en <xref href="System.Activities.Statements.CompensableActivity"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Activities.Statements.Compensate"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Activities.Statements.Compensate"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <xref:System.WorkflowModel.InArgument%601> that contains the <xref:System.Activities.Statements.CompensationHandle> for this <xref href="System.Activities.Statements.Compensate"></xref> activity.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger den <xref:System.WorkflowModel.InArgument%601> som innehåller den <xref:System.Activities.Statements.CompensationHandle>för den här <xref href="System.Activities.Statements.Compensate"> </xref> aktivitet.</xref:System.Activities.Statements.CompensationHandle>

trans-unit.source: When the Target of the <xref:System.Activities.Statements.CompensationHandle> is specified, the <xref:System.Activities.Statements.Compensate> activity explicitly invokes the compensation handler of <xref:System.Activities.Statements.CompensableActivity>, which returns the <xref:System.Activities.Statements.CompensationHandle>.
trans-unit.target: När mål för den <xref:System.Activities.Statements.CompensationHandle>anges <xref:System.Activities.Statements.Compensate>aktivitet explicit anropar kompensationshanteraren, <xref:System.Activities.Statements.CompensableActivity>som returnerar <xref:System.Activities.Statements.CompensationHandle>.</xref:System.Activities.Statements.CompensationHandle> </xref:System.Activities.Statements.CompensableActivity> </xref:System.Activities.Statements.Compensate> </xref:System.Activities.Statements.CompensationHandle>

trans-unit.source: When the Target of the <xref:System.Activities.Statements.CompensationHandle> is not specified, the <xref:System.Activities.Statements.Compensate> activity invokes the default compensation for any child <xref:System.Activities.Statements.CompensableActivity> activities in the reverse order of successful completion.
trans-unit.target: När mål för den <xref:System.Activities.Statements.CompensationHandle>inte anges i <xref:System.Activities.Statements.Compensate>aktivitet anropar standard ersättning för alla underordnade <xref:System.Activities.Statements.CompensableActivity>aktiviteter i omvänd ordning för lyckades.</xref:System.Activities.Statements.CompensableActivity> </xref:System.Activities.Statements.Compensate> </xref:System.Activities.Statements.CompensationHandle>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.> InvalidOperationException?qualifyHint=False&autoUpgrade=True is thrown if the Target refers to a <xref:System.Activities.Statements.CompensableActivity> that was previously confirmed or compensated.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.>InvalidOperationException? qualifyHint = False & autoUpgrade = True genereras om målet refererar till en <xref:System.Activities.Statements.CompensableActivity>som tidigare har bekräftats eller kompenserats.</xref:System.Activities.Statements.CompensableActivity> </xref:System.>

trans-unit.source: This property is read-only at runtime.
trans-unit.target: Den här egenskapen är skrivskyddad vid körning.

trans-unit.source: If the value is set at runtime, an <xref:System.InvalidOperationException> is raised.
trans-unit.target: Om värdet anges vid körning, en <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>utlöses.</xref:System.InvalidOperationException>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.WorkflowModel.InArgument%601> that contains the <xref:System.Activities.Statements.CompensationHandle> for this <xref href="System.Activities.Statements.Compensate"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.WorkflowModel.InArgument%601> som innehåller den <xref:System.Activities.Statements.CompensationHandle>för den här <xref href="System.Activities.Statements.Compensate"> </xref>.</xref:System.Activities.Statements.CompensationHandle>
